<h1>Summary</h1>
<p>After the game “Flappy Bird” by Dong Nguyen became so popular, I said to my friend, “We can do that.” So, we
    designed a similar game with the goals of it being extremely difficult to play yet still a very simple concept. The
    object of the game is to fall through thunder clouds without touching them for as long as you can while collecting
    power ups and other items.</p>

