<h3>Description</h3>
<p>In my game “Parachutez,” the player is falling through the clouds, trying to make it safely to the ground without
    coming into contact with the thunderclouds. Along the way, there are different colored balloons to collect to give
    you extra points. Among the balloons, there are also power ups including ghost and shield. Ghost lets you fall
    through the clouds without dying for a period of time, and the shield gives you protection for one cloud hit. </p>

